'''Mat Lucas''' is an American voice actor who voiced [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]] in ''[[Star Wars: Clone Wars]]'' and a few ''Star Wars ''video games. He is considered an "audio double" of [[Hayden Christensen]]. He also has done editing and other film-related tasks at AFI. Mat has stated that he hopes to do more voice-overs in the future. Despite this, he would be replaced by [[Matt Lanter]], who voiced the character onward.

