==Trivia==
*Mat Lucas was originally going to voice [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin]] in the 2008 show [[Star Wars: The Clone Wars]] as well, and even recorded his lines for the first 6 episodes. However, he was later replaced by [[Matt Lanter]].<ref>[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7PM2A1hkkTc The 2D Anakin ft. Mat Lucas]</ref>

